      <p>Though not carnivores, these wild swine are bad-tempered and usually charge anyone who disturbs them. A <a href="ch73s09.html#MonstersAnimals29">boar</a> is covered in coarse, grayish-black fur. Adult males are about 4 feet long and 3 feet high at the shoulder.</p>
